Brookhaven Medical, Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 27, 2017 3:42 AM ET
Healthcare Equipment and Supplies

Company Overview of Brookhaven Medical, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Brookhaven Medical, Inc., through its subsidiaries, designs, manufactures, and markets medical devices products and technologies. It offers vascular, urology, and advanced wound care medical devices, as well as medical devices for patients suffering with dialysis. Brookhaven Medical, Inc. was incorporated in 2013 and is based in Atlanta, Georgia. It has subsidiaries in Athens, Texas; and Greenville, South Carolina.


3050 Peachtree Road N.W.Two Buckhead PlazaSuite 370Atlanta, GA 30305United StatesFounded in 2013



Phone: 404-205-8282

www.brookhavenmed.com







