Brookhaven Medical, Inc. Key Developments

Brookhaven Medical Inc. Names Scott Jones as Chief Operating Officer
Aug 31 16
Brookhaven Medical Inc. named Scott Jones its chief operating officer. As COO, Jones will be responsible for business development, product development and marketing functions. He will also oversee these functions for the company's Athens, Texas-based Brookhaven Technologies Inc. unit. Jones has worked in health care for more than 20 years. Previously, he founded MedaStrat LLC, a boutique mergers and acquisitions consulting practice focused on medical device companies. Before that, he was executive director for business development for Greatbatch Inc.


Brookhaven Medical Inc. Announces Executive Changes
Jan 14 16
Brookhaven Medical Inc. named Marc Morin as its CFO. From June 2013 to December 2015, Morin served as global controller of EndoChoice Holdings and helped take the company public in June 2015. Before working with EndoChoice, Morin was in public accounting with KPMG. Morin will succeed Ross Dedeyn as CFO of Brookhaven Medical.


